{"tid":1781224,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[百hi成材]民間集會團隊想收集昨晚1212集會嘅意見","createTime":"2019-12-13T03:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T04:03:58.000Z","uid":264429,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"08d66d82ca3bab39be9e8da4618c19c33a38d0b6","tid":1781224,"uid":264429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T03:56:04.000Z","msg":"各位手足大家好<br />\n<br />\n昨晚係民間集會團隊在眾籌後舉辦的首次活動，感謝超過4萬位香港人來臨出席。<br />\n當日眾籌之時承諾的透明公開將會一一兌現，活動財務報告正在準備中，完成後會公開俾大家一同監察。<br />\n<br />\n而家想請大家幫我地百hi成材，如果大家對於昨晚嘅集會有任何意見，不妨留個言，等我地知道我地有咩地方可以改進，多謝大家！<br />\n<br />\n亦歡迎大家follow 我地嘅社交媒體，留意我地未來嘅動向。<br />\nFacebook  <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCATeam&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6v8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=2a367587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam</a><br />\nIG  <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hkcat/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhkcat%2F&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6v8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=dff3a5f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hkcat/</a><br />\nTwitter  <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hkcat/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhkcat%2F&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6v8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=dff3a5f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hkcat/</a><br />\n眾籌網站  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/s/HKCATeam/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fs%2FHKCATeam%2F&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6v8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=eb7eed77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/s/HKCATeam/</a>"},{"pid":"c786ff5a0434ecc1e4e35b380489deb1f4bd648c","tid":1781224,"uid":170812,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T03:56:29.000Z","msg":"感謝左先"},{"pid":"a8b872c44746524b6a7ba90af6739aebf7f1bd41","tid":1781224,