Time":"2019-12-13T04:02:42.000Z","msg":"被濫捕手足最好blackblock埋先上台<br />\n其他都做得好好"},{"pid":"4c4780c289ce4c6eaa7aab40ab6310be0e4f981e","tid":1781224,"uid":14148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T04:16:05.000Z","msg":"唔該晒巴打"},{"pid":"6e74ada02cee80c371c11b9e77208188ef613987","tid":1781224,"uid":273723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5ab1ce62d66f8cae286fa995e65f7b7a9003a13","tid":1781224,"uid":137615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"音響有進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T04:20:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac79ca0896ff166b2a925f891bab53a43227adc","tid":1781224,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T04:21:30.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"8a3747c73d02b2a1bb7e8c675aede73eb9517be7","tid":1781224,"uid":137615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T04:21:35.000Z","msg":"金已貨"},{"pid":"b12e8f507f53ba6e6728eb0f6d5b2a9bc69d51e6","tid":1781224,"uid":137615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T04:24:03.000Z","msg":"你條twitter link打錯 去左ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我估係<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HKCATeam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKCATeam&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6v8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=a28a3764\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HKCATeam</a> ？"},{"pid":"f2bd8f1451b3ebc61f978701eb7f1c174aa034d7","tid":1781224,"uid":83650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T04:24:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4ab344684507a44a80abcc521ad9daf7ac77b36","tid":1781224,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T04:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2067536ae22d3ee303047126c1836990aba3cb","tid":1781224,"uid":273723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T04:26:46.000Z","msg":"上次推圍牆 今次寫信 真係幾有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我覺得應該多D宣傳下未來嘅行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除左請民陣過黎宣布元旦有節目之外<br />\n都應該叫下人入工會啊 聖誕去下window shopping咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家叫口號除左光復香港之外 都應該叫下「組織工會 全民三罷」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d1b4ff3a9413b715c0a7b3221ea2568e576a8ad","tid":1781224,"uid":70771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a371e1133df5666727dba1016ce8f3b44a92e53a","tid":1781224,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T04:02:42.000Z","msg":"被濫捕手足最好blackblock埋先上台<br />\n其他都做得好好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T04:28:45.000Z","msg":"呢樣真，另外音響真係改善左好多，繼續努力，再要錢就出聲，同時都希望大家未來keep住捐維持到落去贏果日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93bbf8588ee84d3a99ab443ad01cc7d2af99cfe","tid":1781224,"uid":273991,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T04:40:03.000Z","msg":"音響真係進步好多<br />\n後面都聽得好清楚<br />\n今次既嘉賓都幾多元化<br />\n好欣賞請左男高音黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n普通市民分享唔該black bloc<br />\n另外我覺得可以係嘉賓出場次序安排下<br />\n尋晚我會覺得號召力比較勁既人都係偏早出場(鄺神/胡志偉/gphone)<br />\n中段由律師/護士分享雖然實用, 但真係有少少悶場, 我眼見好多人係果陣走左, 又或者自己傾計 (唔好屌我, 我知唔係睇show, 我留到最後, 我只係講番當時情況)<br />\n或者可以一開始既時候講下集會流程, 吸引下大家留到最後<br />\n加上愛丁堡真係有d 凍 (近海), 又近AIA (好似2個平行時空咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />), 下次會唔會考慮下遮打?<br />\n<br />\nanythx<br />\n多謝民間集會團隊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c712fbf57ab46d6931be8cb58884191e1e52f3b","tid":1781224,"uid":194363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T04:45:11.000Z","msg":"尋晚音響真係做得好好呀！！！<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"750234c7d2035a5fd3e8006959fcbe193845a422","tid":1781224,"uid":267172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T04:47:11.000Z","msg":"我淨係知個音響好好<br />\n平時啲集會去到郵局唔會聽到聲<br />\n尋日聽到"},{"pid":"4df6b6920772448a7ea9e6682bff7f7d0af454b4","tid":1781224,"uid":73323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T04:50:25.000Z","msg":"做得好好 不過琴日聽到講心理果個女嘉賓開始唔係好聽得明佢想講乜 之後走左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6fa7e175826a54c3bc7c053453b86664e2d51d","tid":1781224,"uid":194363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T04:57:29.000Z","msg":"其實我見到陳傳道上台發言<br />\n我有擔心過佢會被柴台<br />\n始終上次鐘樓事件<br />\n但好彩無事<br />\n<br />\n最意外請到男高音<br />\n<br />\n仲有下次再有集會 可唔可以請許智峯<br />\n<br />\n同意  巴打佢哋講 下次再有被捕手足發言<br />\n一定要black Bloc<br />\n同埋現場用變聲器<br />\n得唔得架？"},{"pid":"30160c0fe8273be8c28116aad537498f06c51175","tid":1781224,"uid":49753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:11:39.000Z","msg":"音響真係好好<br />\n值得繼續課金"},{"pid":"5dd0c753da1f7249626f6e81f65fb89c415d1563","tid":1781224,"uid":264429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b12e8f507f53ba6e6728eb0f6d5b2a9bc69d51e6","tid":1781224,"uid":137615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T04:24:03.000Z","msg":"你條twitter link打錯 去左ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我估係<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HKCATeam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKCATeam&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6v8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=a28a3764\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HKCATeam</a> ？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:14:18.000Z","msg":"Sorry 就上庭緊張打錯<br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c982608ef5d77aad7c4a7956d0328e9f3d071d3","tid":1781224,"uid":133565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:19:08.000Z","msg":"音響好好。加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4413d21fa5c2534bdde14e63d9b8bf1cb68fd0c","tid":1781224,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:20:39.000Z","msg":"琴晚集會內容幾好，繼續加油，如果有能力，試下邀請環保少女來港做個集會"},{"pid":"aad29d674c3ac5e567b432642426f873223ad0a0","tid":1781224,"uid":170199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:22:52.000Z","msg":"樓上都幾多人讚有男高音<br />\n<br />\n不過我就唔係咁睇 唔係話佢唱得唔好 反而係佢唱到咁 台下群眾點樣一齊唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d07521fcb1a58275f5add8b8a5fd8cc38aaef5","tid":1781224,"uid":264429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5ab1ce62d66f8cae286fa995e65f7b7a9003a13","tid":1781224,"uid":137615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"音響有進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:27:04.000Z","msg":"音響方面嘅提升真係全靠各位課金先成就到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ddec0fa973d555a727e7c9db2116d422c55e8f","tid":1781224,"uid":274996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:35:26.000Z","msg":"多謝你地。嘉賓好informative 學到好多野。<br />\n音響好ok, 我係IFC 天橋都聽到少少，現場更加清晰。<br />\n<br />\n如果可以7:30 開始就可以聽埋前面，因為我食完飯先來，miss 咗前面。"},{"pid":"37ecab9b09f8fa4cf2e2cf66d97742b4752b83f0","tid":1781224,"uid":189652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:51:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee038f12ff7864562d4d23bc3b7bc5a7a539c9c7","tid":1781224,"uid":189652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T06:13:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83835f8028d0a9079b1b8512d71fbd005e1ce1ba","tid":1781224,"uid":302944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T06:31:56.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申錢已捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7905b5348566cfe8e23dbc4ee7b33cc977f5cfa","tid":1781224,"uid":10524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T06:34:13.000Z","msg":"有錢係唔同啲<br />\n早就要籌la<br />\n<br />\n同民陣輪住搞真係唔冼停"},{"pid":"9363f5beec30c7896f20342df5396173eb2a12ac","tid":1781224,"uid":228337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T06:47:57.000Z","msg":"音響好咗好多（會唔會好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n好多嘉賓都好好<br />\n資訊類、集氣類、分享經歷類<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得呢種晚間集會<br />\n控制係2個鐘就好<br />\n最盡2個半鐘<br />\n<br />\n個人私心一向幾鍾意聽gphone同jimmy講嘢<br />\n除咗簡短，激勵，有志氣之外<br />\n佢哋一般會分享現況<br />\n同我哋有乜下一步實際行動參與<br />\n唔會淨係講「大家要堅持」之類<br />\n<br />\n我去過其他集會，好怕聽牧師嗰啲講嘢<br />\n聽過某集會傳道人話<br />\n「我哋行到今時今日唔係靠香港人係靠神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n我對呢啲說話係超級反感<br />\n寧願佢正正經經讀經講道唱詩歌<br />\n我並非盲反，「求神繼續帶領」嗰啲我都接受<br />\n今次個傳道ok，講嘢十分之正常<br />\n<br />\n已課金，小小心意"},{"pid":"329588b405ba9515a0a83948db4848814b2b0616","tid":1781224,"uid":236669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T06:49:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">18區遊行！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"d70513cb0d67d5ba425f8439554be9066035cbc7","tid":1781224,"uid":303573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T06:59:45.000Z","msg":"音響改善左好多 ifc天橋都聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請到男高音勁意外 最開心係佢唱廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位講者都講得好好 扣題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時間上要控制得好啲 夜左啲人開始會走同埋坐耐會凍 <br />\n<br />\n辛苦晒民記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44cbb51b0e4adc70e50a6754942d5e915c593b4","tid":1781224,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T11:13:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af08421cf4c4f3f1b2e9b128ae37c5af2a60f8d2","tid":1781224,"uid":210688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T11:27:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c6c9c8adf367a4235c1e348be9aa0b1690e74f","tid":1781224,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T11:37:53.000Z","msg":"和你推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc0d0dd05bc0f1c3babcd8484e33f134d284939","tid":1781224,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T11:38:44.000Z","msg":"和你推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d293e5cd3d2acd34ae281a6303a6dfd57d9fef8","tid":1781224,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T11:40:20.000Z","msg":"音響好似勁得濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4260dfb0360f7d0a54dc6318761c51eca31e19","tid":1781224,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T11:41:58.000Z","msg":"音響好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n流程唔差 不過略嫌長咗啲 覺得集會兩個鐘內完會好啲"},{"pid":"1f4cd577b6243fc6e93a2cbd570e69330cba9058","tid":1781224,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T11:45:47.000Z","msg":"支持，感谢， 搞一次新疆"},{"pid":"dc64f6bbecaa1e6b9262717174c682669a75190d","tid":1781224,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T12:04:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a110de90e547397073025dbfe36d065186353a01","tid":1781224,"uid":264429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b93bbf8588ee84d3a99ab443ad01cc7d2af99cfe","tid":1781224,"uid":273991,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T04:40:03.000Z","msg":"音響真係進步好多<br />\n後面都聽得好清楚<br />\n今次既嘉賓都幾多元化<br />\n好欣賞請左男高音黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n普通市民分享唔該black bloc<br />\n另外我覺得可以係嘉賓出場次序安排下<br />\n尋晚我會覺得號召力比較勁既人都係偏早出場(鄺神/胡志偉/gphone)<br />\n中段由律師/護士分享雖然實用, 但真係有少少悶場, 我眼見好多人係果陣走左, 又或者自己傾計 (唔好屌我, 我知唔係睇show, 我留到最後, 我只係講番當時情況)<br />\n或者可以一開始既時候講下集會流程, 吸引下大家留到最後<br />\n加上愛丁堡真係有d 凍 (近海), 又近AIA (好似2個平行時空咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />), 下次會唔會考慮下遮打?<br />\n<br />\nanythx<br />\n多謝民間集會團隊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T12:06:50.000Z","msg":"嘉賓出場次序方面，要遷就嘉賓既時間，唔係咁易編排，下次會再努力...<br />\n<br />\n至於遮打，popo成日話個場太細唔批..."},{"pid":"8234b9b94c2e0c79e110ba6944f21455c568850f","tid":1781224,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T12:19:03.000Z","msg":"多謝你 請你keep住攪"}]}